{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly, we heard calls, 'Halt!,' which means stop and being shot at.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow-- somehow, we came across a farmer who was on the fields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He grabbed a hold of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wiggled out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He grabbed a hold of my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is only seconds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It couldn't have been much longer, because they've been running after me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I begged him to release her, and I tried to give him money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We always had some money on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know how much, or whatever-- had to give him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he wouldn't release her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he says, look, they're behind you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And with remembering that, I just pulled my sister again, and I ran out around a little forest in the distance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I must have passed out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the only thing I can-- all I remember is being shot, fired at, and 'Halt!, Halt!",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Halt!' And when I got up, I saw nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everything was just bare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I must have still been dazed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I lay there for a while and started walking in the forest, coming across little groups who obviously managed to do the same thing that I did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you heard-- in the night, you heard the cries from the train-- it must have been near the train station-- the cries and the firing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we kept on wandering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We kept on walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the only thing I could follow was the electric poles, or the telegraph poles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I didn't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we wandered around for-- for a while-- for-- for a good many weeks like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And came across little [INAUDIBLE] in groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They wouldn't-- didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Other groups didn't want me either, because the more people, the more-- more danger.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
